data.description: Experience the epitome of modern living at this stunning property. This residence boasts an array of desirable features, including gleaming flooring, ample closets throughout and a spacious living area designed for comfort and relaxation. The first floor includes a convenient bedroom with a full bathroom, perfect for versatile living arrangements. The open-concept kitchen-living area, complete with a stylish kitchen island, is an ideal space for entertaining and everyday living. Second floor features a primary bedroom with vaulted ceiling and double closets, a second bedroom and a full bathroom with tub. With a total of three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, this property offers the perfect blend of functionality and luxury. Additional highlights include a basement for storage, a shed, a back yard with patio offering a private retreat for relaxation or entertaining. Close proximity to shopping centers and major highways. Don't miss the chance to make this property your Home !
